 against branch origin/trunk&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14312603" author="omkreddy" created="Mon, 9 Feb 2015 18:43:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching a patch which handles NumberFormatException while reading   recovery checkpoint file. We still fail for other IOExceptions. On NumberFormatException we will set the last recovery point to zero.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
